<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>

<body style="margin: 0;background: whitesmoke;">


    <div style=" font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom: 1rem; padding-top: 1rem;">
        <div
            style="width: 90%; max-width: 32rem;margin: 0 auto;text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; background: white; border-top: 5px solid #f35327;">
            <h1 style="font-size: 1rem; text-transform: capitalize;">Hi {{username}},</h1>
            <div style="font-weight: bold;text-align: center;">We're glad to let you know that your Debit Card is ready.
                Please find below the details of your card.</div>
            <h2 style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Card Details</h2>
            <div style="background-color: whitesmoke;padding: 0.5rem;">
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Card Type:</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto; text-transform: capitalize;">{{cardtype}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Card Holder Name:</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{cardholder}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Card Number:</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{cardno}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Card Cvv</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{cardcvv}}</div>
                </div>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; justify-content: space-between;padding: 0.5rem;">
                    <div style="text-align: left;">Card Expiry</div>
                    <div style="width: fit-content; margin-left: auto;">{{cardexp}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid lightgrey;margin-bottom: 1rem;">NB: After receiving this email, kindly login and goto settings to find your card under debit cards and activate it!</div>
            <div style="padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid lightgrey;margin-bottom: 1rem;">{{date}}</div>
            <div>
                If you did not request for this, kindly contact Pinerock Credit Union support at
                support@pinerockcreditunion.com or simply reply to this email.</div>
            <div>
                Warm regards, Pinerock Credit Union.</div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>